**1. ArmOperation.cs** — Add `[DynamicallyAccessedMembers]` to the generic parameter `T` on `IsResource<T>()`, `Rehydrate<T>()`, and `RehydrateAsync<T>()`. Also add `using System.Diagnostics.CodeAnalysis;` if not already present.

